description:
In this video, we're going to help you take the name of jesus with you wherever you go! With our top gospel karaoke selection, we'll have you singing your heart out in no time.
Not a gospel fan? That's okay! We've got plenty of other great karaoke selections to choose from. Whether you're looking for a fun night out with friends or a private party for you and your loved ones, we've got you covered. So come on over and let's get baptised in the river of life!

Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters Youtube channel.

#KaraokeLyrics #ClassicHymn #3Sisters
